{"segment":1,"line_start":1,"line_end":100,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_jing_jun","speaker_name":"荆俊","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"是咸阳第一美人寡妇清！","tone":"激动","chapter":123,"line_start":10,"line_end":12},{"speaker":"char_lv_bu_wei","speaker_name":"吕不韦","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"少龙你为何如此莽撞，未向我请示，竟向大王提议任徐先这不识时务的家伙做左丞相，破坏我的大计，难道我走开一阵子都不行吗？","tone":"愤怒","chapter":123,"line_start":18,"line_end":20},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_lv_bu_wei","text":"那时大王要立即决定人选，相国又不知何时归来，可是少龙的提议却是绝对为吕相着想，只有让秦人分享权力，才能显出吕相胸怀广阔，不是任用私人之辈。这么一来，秦廷谁还敢说吕相闲话？","tone":"陈述","chapter":123,"line_start":22,"line_end":24},{"speaker":"char_lv_bu_wei","speaker_name":"吕不韦","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"少龙推辞了这仅次于我的职位，是否亦为同样的理由呢？","tone":"疑问","chapter":123,"line_start":26,"line_end":28},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_lv_bu_wei","text":"吕相对我们乌家恩重如山，个人荣辱算得什么？","tone":"恳求","chapter":123,"line_start":30,"line_end":32},{"speaker":"char_lv_bu_wei","speaker_name":"吕不韦","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"我有三个女儿，最小的叫吕娘蓉，就把她许配与你吧！好补替倩公主的位置。","tone":"陈述","chapter":123,"line_start":34,"line_end":36},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_lv_bu_wei","text":"吕相请收回成命，少龙现在心如死灰，再不想涉及嫁娶之事，误了小姐的终身。","tone":"恳求","chapter":123,"line_start":50,"line_end":52},{"speaker":"char_jia_jiang","speaker_name":"家将","listener":"char_lv_bu_wei","text":"相爷，大事不好，魏人信陵君率领燕、赵、韩、楚、魏五国联军，大破我军于大河之西，蒙大将军败返函谷关，联军正兵临关外。","tone":"焦急","chapter":123,"line_start":54,"line_end":56},{"speaker":"char_lv_bu_wei","speaker_name":"吕不韦","listener":null,"text":"此事大大不妙，我要立即进宫晋见大王。","tone":"焦急","chapter":123,"line_start":60,"line_end":60},{"speaker":"char_tao_fang","speaker_name":"陶方","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"有个自称是少龙故交的汉子在等你，他怎知你今天会回来呢？","tone":"疑问","chapter":123,"line_start":66,"line_end":68},{"speaker":"char_long_yang_jun","speaker_name":"龙阳君","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"董兄果是惦念旧情的人，没有舍弃故人。","tone":"微笑","chapter":123,"line_start":86,"line_end":88},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_long_yang_jun","text":"终瞒你不过。","tone":"苦笑","chapter":123,"line_start":90,"line_end":90}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_xiang_shao_long","name":"项少龙","alias":["董马痴"],"identity":"穿越者、秦国太傅","faction":"乌家","role":"protagonist","archetype":"warrior","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"穿越至战国的现代人，智勇双全，深得秦王信任","personality":{"traits":["机智","重情重义","善于应变","淡泊名利","勇敢果断","心思缜密"],"speech_style":"沉稳得体，善于言辞","temperament":"外冷内热"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_lv_bu_wei","type":"宿敌","intensity":80,"bond_level":2,"dynamic":"表面臣服实则对立"},{"target":"char_teng_yi","type":"挚友","intensity":85,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"生死之交"},{"target":"char_jing_jun","type":"挚友","intensity":80,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"兄弟情谊"},{"target":"char_long_yang_jun","type":"合作者","intensity":60,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"互相帮助"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[123],"source_refs":[{"chapter":123,"line_start":2,"line_end":2,"text":"项少龙、滕翼、荆俊偕同十八铁卫返回咸阳"}]},{"id":"char_lv_bu_wei","name":"吕不韦","alias":["右丞相","吕相"],"identity":"秦国右丞相","faction":"秦国朝堂","role":"villain","archetype":"scholar","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"权倾大秦的奸商丞相，野心勃勃，手段狠辣","personality":{"traits":["野心勃勃","心狠手辣","老谋深算","独断专行","善于笼络","猜忌多疑"],"speech_style":"威严霸道，喜怒无常","temperament":"阴沉"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_xiang_shao_long","type":"宿敌","intensity":80,"bond_level":2,"dynamic":"欲收为己用"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[123],"source_refs":[{"chapter":123,"line_start":18,"line_end":18,"text":"这个正权倾大秦的人物道"}]},{"id":"char_teng_yi","name":"滕翼","alias":[],"identity":"项少龙挚友","faction":"乌家","role":"companion","archetype":"warrior","rank":"略有小成","one_line":"项少龙的忠实战友，一同出生入死","personality":{"traits":["忠诚","勇猛","沉稳","寡言","重义气"],"speech_style":"简洁有力","temperament":"沉稳"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_xiang_shao_long","type":"挚友","intensity":85,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"生死之交"}],"known_s