{"segment":2,"line_start":101,"line_end":200,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_long_yang_jun","speaker_name":"龙阳君","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"董马痴怎会这么不明不白地轻易死掉，项少龙更不会完全没出过手便溜回咸阳，我还特别派人到楚国印证此事，刚好真的董马痴全族被夷狄杀害，别人或会以为那是疑兵之计，但我却知道真的董马痴确已死掉，假的董马痴仍在咸阳风流快活，否则赵致亦不会溜回咸阳会她的夫郎了。","tone":"陈述","chapter":123,"line_start":92,"line_end":94},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_long_yang_jun","text":"信陵君刚大破秦军，君上可知此来是多么危险？","tone":"担心","chapter":123,"line_start":96,"line_end":98},{"speaker":"char_long_yang_jun","speaker_name":"龙阳君","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"怎会不知道？我正因秦军败北，才要匆匆赶来。","tone":"陈述","chapter":123,"line_start":100,"line_end":100},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_long_yang_jun","text":"雅夫人好吗？","tone":"无奈","chapter":123,"line_start":102,"line_end":102},{"speaker":"char_long_yang_jun","speaker_name":"龙阳君","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"是赵雅托我交你之物，以示她对你的爱永不改变，永恒如玉，只是限于环境，又不愿令你为难，才忍心不到咸阳来寻你，希望你明白她的苦心。","tone":"柔声","chapter":123,"line_start":104,"line_end":106},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_long_yang_jun","text":"君上来此，有何贵干？","tone":"沉声","chapter":123,"line_start":108,"line_end":110},{"speaker":"char_long_yang_jun","speaker_name":"龙阳君","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"还不是为了被软禁在咸阳做质子的敝国太子增，今天秦兵大败，秦人必会迁怒于他，要杀之泄愤。我们大王最爱此子，奴家唯有冒死营救。","tone":"无奈","chapter":123,"line_start":112,"line_end":114},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_long_yang_jun","text":"君上想我项少龙怎样帮忙？","tone":"疑问","chapter":123,"line_start":118,"line_end":118},{"speaker":"char_long_yang_jun","speaker_name":"龙阳君","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"现在秦君和吕不韦对项兄宠信有加，只要项兄美言两句，说不定可保敝国太子增一命。","tone":"恳求","chapter":123,"line_start":120,"line_end":122},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_long_yang_jun","text":"君上放心，冲着我们的交情，我会尽力而为。","tone":"豪迈","chapter":123,"line_start":124,"line_end":124},{"speaker":"char_tao_fang","speaker_name":"陶方","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"大王召少龙入宫议事。","tone":"陈述","chapter":123,"line_start":128,"line_end":130},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_long_yang_jun","text":"龙兄请留在这里等候消息。","tone":"陈述","chapter":123,"line_start":132,"line_end":132},{"speaker":"char_an_gu_xi","speaker_name":"安谷傒","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"项太傅一力举荐徐将军当左丞相，我们禁卫都非常感激。","tone":"认真","chapter":123,"line_start":142,"line_end":144},{"speaker":"char_zhuang_xiang_wang","speaker_name":"庄襄王","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"项太傅平身！","tone":"陈述","chapter":123,"line_start":162,"line_end":162},{"speaker":"char_zhuang_xiang_wang","speaker_name":"庄襄王","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"少龙可知寡人急召卿来，所为何事？","tone":"疑问","chapter":123,"line_start":182,"line_end":184},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_zhuang_xiang_wang","text":"请恕微臣愚鲁！","tone":"陈述","chapter":123,"line_start":192,"line_end":192},{"speaker":"char_xu_xian","speaker_name":"徐先","listener":"char_zhuang_xiang_wang","text":"大王请三思此事！","tone":"沉声","chapter":123,"line_start":194,"line_end":194},{"speaker":"char_du_bi","speaker_name":"杜璧","listener":"char_zhuang_xiang_wang","text":"五国联军锐气方殷，若弃函谷关之险，妄然出战，一旦败北，恐函谷关也不保，那时联军长驱直进，大秦基业怕要毁于一旦，此刻实宜守不宜攻。","tone":"严肃","chapter":123,"line_start":198,"line_end":200}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_zhao_ya","name":"赵雅","alias":["雅夫人"],"identity":"赵国女子","faction":"赵国","role":"companion","archetype":"healer","rank":"平平无奇","one_line":"项少龙的旧爱，因环境所限不能来咸阳，托龙阳君转交玉镯","personality":{"traits":["深情","忍耐","温柔","善解人意","坚强"],"speech_style":"未开口","temperament":"温柔"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_xiang_shao_long","type":"恋人","intensity":90,"bond_level":5,"dynamic":"被迫分离"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[123],"source_refs":[{"chapter":123,"line_start":104,"line_end":104,"text":"是赵雅托我交你之物"}]},{"id":"char_xin_ling_jun_wei_wu_ji","name":"信陵君魏无忌","alias":["无忌公子","信陵君","无忌小儿"],"identity":"魏国公子","faction":"魏国","role":"villain","archetype":"scholar","rank":"出神入化","one_line":"足智多谋的魏国公子，率五国联军大破秦军，与魏王不和","personality":{"traits":["足智多谋","野心勃勃","善于统兵","名震六国","心狠手辣"],"speech_style":"未开口","temperament":"阴沉"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[123],"source_refs":[{"chapter":123,"line_start":54,"line_end":54,"text":"魏人信陵君率领燕、赵、韩、楚、魏五国联军"}]},{"id":"char_tai_zi_zeng","name":"太子增","alias":["魏增","敝国太子增"],"identity":"魏国太子","faction":"魏国","role":"npc","archetype":"scholar","rank":"平平无奇","one_line":"魏国太子，在咸阳做质子，后被项少龙与龙阳君设计救出","personality":{"traits":["懦弱","胆小","可怜","无辜","依赖他人"],"speech_style":"未开口","temperament":"恐惧"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_long_yang_jun","type":"合作者","intensity":40,"bond_level":2,"dynamic":"被营救"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[123],"source_refs":[{"chapter":123,"line_start":112,"line_end":112,"text":"被软禁在咸阳做质子的敝国太子增"}]},{"id":"char_zhuang_xiang_wang","name":"庄襄王","alias":["大王","秦君"],"identity":"秦国国君","faction":"秦国朝堂","role":"npc","archetype":"scholar","rank":"平平无奇","one_line":"秦国国君，对项少龙宠信有加，气定神闲","personality":{"traits":["英明","果断","信任臣下","沉稳","有威严"],"speech_style":"威严柔和","temperament":"沉稳"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_xiang_shao_long","type":"合作者","intensity":60,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"宠信"},{"target":"char_lv_bu_wei","type":"合作者","intensity":50,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"依赖"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[123],"source_refs":[{"chapter":123,"line_start":156,"line_end":156,"text":"庄襄王高踞大殿尽端两层台阶之上的龙座"}]},{"id":"char_an_gu_xi","name":"安谷傒","alias":[],"identity":"秦宫禁卫统领","faction":"秦国朝堂","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"略有小成","one_line":"秦宫禁卫统领，高俊威武，对项少龙有惺惺相惜之意","personality":{"traits":["英武","忠诚","正直","惺惺相惜","尽职"],"speech_style":"低声诚恳","temperament":"沉稳"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_xiang_shao_long","type":"合作者","intensity":40,"bond_level":2,"dynamic":"惺惺相惜"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[123],"source_refs":[{"chapter":123,"line_start":136,"line_end":136,"text":"秦宫的禁卫统领安谷傒破天荒首次在宫门候他"}]},{"id":"char_xu_xian","name":"徐先","alias":["徐将军","左丞相"],"identity":"秦国左丞相","faction":"秦国朝堂","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"略有小成","one_line":"秦国军方德高望重之人，被项少龙举荐为左丞相","personality":{"traits":["刚正不阿","不畏权势","直言敢谏","沉稳","有威望"],"speech_style":"肃容沉声","temperament":"严肃"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_xiang_shao_long","type":"合作者","intensity":50,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"感激敬重"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[123],"source_refs":[{"chapter":123,"line_start":148,"line_end":148,"text":"徐先乃秦国军方德高望重的人"}]},{"id":"char_wang_ling","name":"王陵","alias":[],"identity":"秦国大将","faction":"秦国朝堂","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"略有小成","one_line":"秦国军方要人，与王龁、徐先同等级资历","personality":{"traits":["沉稳","忠勇","老成","正直","寡言"],"speech_style":"未开口","temperament":"沉稳"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[123],"source_refs":[{"chapter":123,"line_start":158,"line_end":158,"text":"他只认得大将王陵"}]},{"id":"char_cai_ze","name":"蔡泽","alias":["关中君"],"identity":"秦国关中君","faction":"秦国朝堂","role":"npc","archetype":"scholar","rank":"平平无奇","one_line":"吕不韦任前的右丞相，为人面面俱到，仍受重用","personality":{"traits":["圆滑","面面俱到","老练","谨慎","识时务"],"speech_style":"未开口","temperament":"沉稳"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_lv_bu_wei","type":"合作者","intensity":40,"bond_level":2,"dynamic":"被取代后仍受重用"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[123],"source_refs":[{"chapter":123,"line_start":158,"line_end":158,"text":"关中君蔡泽"}]},{"id":"char_du_bi","name":"杜璧","alias":["将军杜璧"],"identity":"秦国将军","faction":"秦国朝堂","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"略有小成","one_line":"拥秦王次子成蟜阵营的将军，对项少龙态度冷淡","personality":{"traits":["固执","有城府","对立","谨慎","有野心"],"speech_style":"严肃","temperament":"严肃"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_xiang_shao_long","type":"对手","intensity":40,"bond_level":1,"dynamic":"冷淡对立"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[123],"source_refs":[{"chapter":123,"line_start":158,